				<td colspan="2"><span>Natureboy's post contains the only official definition of killstealing. It mentions nothing about damage. And yes, KSing occurs in WoS all the time, but unless a GM sees it happen they will not get into trouble about it. Any zone of that design, with camps at the walls and free-roaming named mobs will be that way. And if you believe in &quot;playing nice&quot; it's usually best to avoid them.
