				<td colspan="2"><span>However if you are a bard KSing is a fun thing to deal with, we get a nifty lil song called highsun... Nextime the sob KS's something that is clearly yours, follow the mob. Let him get it down to about 20% then highsun it, it'll go right back to 33% and to its spawn point. He'll still have agro and get summoned if its a summoner, if not just keep on doing this till he gets tired and runs outta mana.
<br />

<br />

<br />
Another trick to pull, if its a mob you can charm, charm it and then break the charm and finish it off out of his range, you'll get the exp. &quot;charming and breaking resets damage lists&quot;
